snippet.title: Bad Guys at School Gameplay Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
In Bad Guys at School you can play as students and revolt against school system, or decide to become a teacher that must maintain order despite the violence and brutality in the school.

Steam Link - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1218280/Bad_Guys_at_School/
